project_descr: ENHANCING INFRASTRUCTURE DEVELOPMENT THROUGH (PPP) PUBLIC PRIVATE PARTNERSHIP

outputs.output_descr: The project ultimate goal is to support the Syrian Government’s National PPP Programme aiming at developing the infrastructures in Syria.  Under the umbrella of the National Strategy for Public Private Partnership, the project will seek the cooperation between the public and the private sector in order to develop the needed infrastructure.
